121	<main>\n <section>\n  <div>\n   <div>\n    <div>\n     <span>Engineering</span> <span>·</span> <span title="Estonia, Georgia, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Latvia, Lithuania, Moldova, Montenegro, Romania, Portugal, Netherlands, Ukraine, Spain, Azerbaijan, Bulgaria, Croatia, Turkey, Italy, Portugal, Poland">Multiple locations</span> <span>·</span> <span> Fully Remote </span>\n    </div>\n    <h1><span>Frontend Engineer (Remote)</span></h1>\n    <div></div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <div>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong>Let’s Enhance</strong> is an innovative AI startup that specializes in image enhancement technology. We use cutting-edge artificial intelligence and machine learning algorithms to enhance, upscale images as well as generate scenes for products without compromising quality. Our mission is to empower individuals and businesses to transform their visual content through advanced technology.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">We’re an AI imaging company with two products: <strong>LetsEnhance.io</strong> — a platform for high-quality image upscaling and enhancement with over 1M monthly active users, and <strong>Claid.ai</strong>, an AI-powered toolkit for creating beautiful product visuals. In this role, you’ll primarily focus on Claid.ai, working on advanced frontend features for a fast-evolving, image-generation workflow.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Let's Enhance is supported by Techstars, Nvidia and Google, and was twice rated as the top product on Product Hunt. More than <strong>5M people worldwide</strong> use our products, and our API automates image enhancement for Fortune 500 companies.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">We are 25+ people, located in 15 countries and speaking 10+ languages.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr"></p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Let's Enhance is looking for a talented and experienced <strong>Frontend Engineer</strong> to join our dynamic team. As the Frontend Engineer, you will play a crucial role in shaping the user experience of our platform and driving the development of our web-based image enhancement service.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">We work async-first, with minimal meetings and documented processes to support collaboration across time zones.\n    <br>\n    <br></p>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong><em>We expect you to: </em></strong></p>\n   <br>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong>I</strong>mplement new frontend components and features.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Work closely with the product team to create user-friendly and visually appealing interfaces that meet user needs and enhance the overall user experience.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Ensure quality of the implemented features: conduct code reviews and perform end-to-end testing.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Collaborate with team members, including backend developers, product managers, and ML team, to ensure seamless integration of frontend and backend components.</p>\n   <ul></ul>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong>You’re a perfect candidate if you have:</strong></p>\n   <p dir="ltr">At least 4+ years of experience in frontend development.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Strong proficiency in modern frontend technologies, including Typescript and React.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Knowledge of UI/UX design principles and the ability to work closely with designers to implement user-friendly interfaces.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Experience with responsive web design and mobile optimization.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Excellent problem-solving and communication skills.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Strong attention to detail and a passion for creating exceptional user experiences.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Product mindset: you're committed to building the best user experience; share values of product development.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">At least Upper Intermediate - Advanced English level (B2-C1).</p>\n   <ul></ul>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong>Our current tech stack:</strong> Typescript, React, Redux, Redux-Saga, Gatsby, Storybook, PostCSS.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong>What does Let’s Enhance offer you?</strong></p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Attractive salary + equity (employee stock options).</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Working shoulder to shoulder with founders.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">An environment without bureaucracy, and a culture where your voice is highly valued.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">An international and diverse team.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Ability to work from anywhere in the world.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Unlimited vacation and sick days.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr">Access to some of the top-notch tech people around the world through our network.</p>\n   <ul></ul>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong>Type of employment:</strong> Full-time independent contractor for an indefinite period.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong>Location</strong>: Fully remote.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong>Our main timezone: </strong>CET (+-2 hours); flexible schedule.</p>\n   <p dir="ltr"><strong><em>What to expect during our "hiring trip":</em></strong></p>\n   <ul>\n    <li>HR Interview</li>\n    <li>Test task</li>\n    <li>Interview with Team Lead</li>\n    <li>Virtual coffee-time with CTO</li>\n    <li>Offer 🎉</li>\n   </ul>\n   <p dir="ltr"><em>Looking forward to getting to know you!</em></p>\n  </div>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <div>\n   <dl>\n    <dt>Department</dt>\n    <dd>Engineering</dd>\n    <dt>Locations</dt>\n    <dd>\n     <span title="Estonia, Georgia, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Latvia, Lithuania, Moldova, Montenegro, Romania, Portugal, Netherlands, Ukraine, Spain, Azerbaijan, Bulgaria, Croatia, Turkey, Italy, Portugal, Poland">Multiple locations</span>\n    </dd>\n    <dt>Remote status</dt>\n    <dd>Fully Remote</dd>\n   </dl>\n  </div>\n </section>\n <section id="section-15212419"></section>\n <section id="section-15212420"></section>\n <section id="section-15212421"></section>\n <section>\n  <div>\n   <div>\n    <div>\n     <div>\n      <span>Engineering</span> <span>·</span> <span title="Estonia, Georgia, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Latvia, Lithuania, Moldova, Montenegro, Romania, Portugal, Netherlands, Ukraine, Spain, Azerbaijan, Bulgaria, Croatia, Turkey, Italy, Portugal, Poland">Multiple locations</span> <span>·</span> <span> Fully Remote </span>\n     </div>\n     <h1><span>Frontend Engineer (Remote)</span></h1>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </section>\n <div></div>\n</main>	Software Engineering	https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/let-s-enhance/jobs/54901173-frontend-engineer-remote#content	https://cdn.getro.com/companies/5ae13aaf-d1db-5811-93a5-f3750a6bc837-1747877851	Let's Enhance	https://careers.letsenhance.io/jobs/6208667-frontend-engineer-remote?utm_source=Techstars+job+board&utm_medium=getro.com&gh_src=Techstars+job+board	Frontend Engineer (Remote)	1753131600	{Media,Photography,"11 - 50 employees",Seed,"Mid-Senior Level"}	{}
122	<section>\n <div>\n  <b>About Outreach</b>\n </div>\n <div>\n  <span>Outreach, founded in 2014, is the only complete AI Revenue Workflow Platform that helps sales leaders benefit from connected account visibility, performance insights, and higher forecasting accuracy across every GTM team. Outreach infuses agentic AI to power 100s of use cases across sales motions. From new logo prospecting to renewal and expansion, Outreach AI automates workflows and frees sellers to focus on more strategic conversations and actions. Global organizations use Outreach to power their revenue teams, including SAP, Siemens, Snowflake, ZoomInfo, and Verizon to name a few. To learn more, please visit </span><a href="http://www.outreach.io/">www.outreach.io</a><span>.</span>\n </div>\n <div>\n  <b>About the Role:</b>\n </div>\n <div>\n  <span>Reporting to the Chief Revenue Officer, the </span><b>Head of AI Value Strategy </b><span>will be responsible for meeting with C-Suite industry leaders to uncover their pain points and deliver strategy and solutions using Outreach’s platform, specifically our AI functionality.This role will work with some of the most forward-thinking company leaders in the world and play a key customer facing role in scaling how we position and sell our product. This role will also play a key role in educating our sales team as a whole on how to sell AI products with an emphasis on value outcomes. </span>\n </div>\n <div>\n  <span> </span>\n </div>\n <div>\n  <span>Ideal candidates bring a background in AI development/engineering, sales engineering, sales management, value consulting or revenue strategy, and can credibly speak to top company leaders in varying industries. Candidates must understand not just how AI works—but how to educate the market, sell it, defend it, and operationalize it in high-stakes sales cycles. Top candidates will understand how AI and specifically Outreach’s product can solve real world business problems. </span>\n </div>\n <div>\n  <span>Location: Open to remote within the US.</span>\n </div>\n</section>\n<section>\n <h3>Key Responsibilities</h3>\n <ul>\n  <li><b>GTM Strategy &amp; Execution </b></li>\n  <li>Lead strategic value engagements with prospective and current enterprise customers, focusing on aligning our AI solutions with their top business priorities and challenges. You’ll guide discussions that uncover economic, operational, and competitive drivers.</li>\n  <li>Help lead end-to-end go-to-market planning for Outreach AI features and solutions.</li>\n  <li>Aid in defining packaging, value messaging, and sales plays aligned to priority segments and verticals.</li>\n  <li>In Partnership with the Enablement team, create sales enablement content and training to ensure AI capabilities are positioned as deal accelerators.</li>\n  <li><b>Sales Leadership &amp; Field Enablement </b></li>\n  <li>Partner closely with sales and enablement to coach managers, SEs, and AEs on how to articulate the value of AI in discovery, demos, and proof-of-value engagements.</li>\n  <li>Assist in creating battlecards and objection-handling tools that help teams confidently navigate AI-focused evaluation cycles.</li>\n  <li><b>Competitive Differentiation </b></li>\n  <li>Develop positioning frameworks to clearly differentiate Outreach AI from: New AI-native platforms entering the sales tech space, Internal AI solutions being built by customers' RevOps or IT teams using LLMs, BI platforms, or open-source tools</li>\n  <li>Build competitive plays and partner with product marketing to arm the field with intel, win stories, and proof points.</li>\n  <li>Establish thought leadership by contributing to whitepapers, customer success stories, and event presentations that illustrate the transformative business value of our AI platform.</li>\n  <li><b>Performance &amp; Value Impact </b></li>\n  <li>Track AI-influenced pipeline and revenue in partnership with RevOps.</li>\n  <li>Build customer value realization stories that 