190	<div>\n <div>Engineering Manager, Marketplace</div>\n <div>\n  <div>\n   <i></i>\n   <div>\n    <span>Remote</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div>\n   <i></i>\n   <div>Engineering</div>\n  </div>\n  <div>\n   <i></i>\n   <div>Remote</div>\n  </div>\n  <div>\n   <i></i>\n   <div>Full-time</div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div>\n  <div>\n   <h3><strong>About Veho</strong></h3>\n   <div>\n    <span>Veho is on a mission to revolutionize the post-purchase experience. We’re building a new, end-to-end logistics infrastructure—from middle mile to last mile—powered by tech that puts customers first. By removing the pain points in delivery and returns, Veho creates deeper loyalty and trust between brands and their customers. Our rapidly growing client list includes leading consumer brands like Hello Fresh, Zara, Macy’s, Sephora, and more.</span>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <span>We’re proud of our championship culture, best-in-class benefits and the chance for every team member to share in our success through equity. Whether you work at one of our facilities or remotely, at Veho you’ll join a mission-driven team that’s transforming logistics—and having a lot of fun along the way.</span>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <strong>About The Role</strong>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <span>As the Software Engineering Manager for Veho’s Marketplace teams, you’ll lead the strategy and execution for the team as they work closely with Product to build out features and functionality in our pricing, offering and routing APIs, as well as internal UIs and driver facing mobile applications. You will partner with product, engineering, DS, and operations stakeholders to deliver impact in the marketplace and route building spaces, including how driver partners claim routes, how Veho fairly prices effort for deliveries and how Veho incentives drivers to deliver top tier consumer experiences. On a daily basis, you will help the team solve tactical problems that improve and redefine the marketplace experience.