310	<main id="main">\n <div>\n  <div>\n   <div aria-multiline="true" aria-label="Start typing to edit text" aria-disabled="true" role="textbox">\n    <span></span>\n    <div>\n     <div>\n      <div>\n       <div>\n        <div></div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <h1 aria-label="Start typing to edit text" role="textbox" tabindex="0"><span>👩‍💻</span><span>🧑🏽‍💻</span> Founding Engineer / Lead Engineer</h1>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n       <div>\n        <div aria-label="View/hide details" tabindex="0" role="button">View details</div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div>\n      <div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <h3>AI Agents to Bridge the Gap between Engineering &amp; Purchasing to reduce manufacturing wast</h3>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <span>Contact</span>: Helena Most [helena@resourcly.earth;<a tabindex="0" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/erikmuttersbach/"><span> LinkedIn</span></a>]\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div role="note">\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <div>\n             <div>\n              <div>\n               <span aria-label="Callout icon" role="img">💸</span>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <div>\n             <div>\n              <div>\n               <span>Referral bonus:</span> If you know someone exceptional feel free to connect us via the mail above, if we end up hiring them, you’ll receive 2,500€.\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           My co-founder <a tabindex="0" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ian-draxten-50992412/"><span>Ian</span></a> and I combine over 15 years of industry experience, working with companies like SEW-Eurodrive, Terex, Bosch and Carl Zeiss. We co-founded<a tabindex="0" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://forto.com/"><span> </span></a><a tabindex="0" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.resourcly.earth/"><span>Resourcly</span></a>, a Techstars-backed, industrial tech startup to help industrial manufacturers streamline complex portfolios to improve EBIT while preventing and reducing idle inventory from being scrapped.\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>With our solution we want to solve industry problems that we have tried to address for the last decade in the manufacturing companies we worked for, but that have so far been out of reach. With newes technology and AI, that can finally happen.</div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>Complex processes and products, lack of engineering talent and massive labor costs as well as a lack of intelligent automation have remained the industry’s most pressing challenge. With LLMs and agents, we finally have the tools to solve this.</div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>Our vision is that future purchasing and engineering processes will be orchestrated and run by an AI workforce - ensuring reliable and cost-efficient procurement and flow of goods in an uncertain and complicated world with finite resources.</div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <span>🦾</span> <span>We're already live with global manufacturing leaders in Europe</span>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <span>💰</span> <span>Backed by one of Europe's top early-stage funds</span>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <span>📈</span> <span>Growing fast and hiring exceptional talent to join early </span>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           Our goal is to build a small, but excellent team, therefore we are<span> looking for a Engineering Lead / Founding Engineer</span>. If you are excited to work in a very early-stage environment alongside the founders, stellar data scientists and engineers, using AI at the product core to solve meaningful problems - please reach out.\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div></div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <h4><span><span>🧠</span> The Role</span></h4>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Lead customer conversations</span> and translate insights into product features and tech strategy.\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Design and build full-stack</span>, while continuously pushing the AI capabilities of our product\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Building scalable</span>, high-quality products\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Lead the ideation, conceptualization and definition of architecture</span> and tech roadmap\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Execution of the tech roadmap, </span>working closely with sales, product team and developers to prioritise developments in alignment with the business strategy\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Take an active role in shaping the product</span>, tech, and the company’s direction.\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <h4><span><span>🧑‍🚀</span> Who You Are</span></h4>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Take full ownership of tech</span>, from concept to deployment and do whatever it takes to get the job done.\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Write code fast </span>and scrap it even faster, but know when to transition to building for scale and quality.\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Enjoy talking to customers</span> and iterating based on feedback.\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Are willing to work hard</span>, to create something new and groundbreaking.\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <h4><span><span>🛠</span> What You Bring</span></h4>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Very strong software engineering background</span>, with expertise in Node.js/TypeScript, and React/TypeScript and versatility in Python\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Strong practical experience with models</span>, LLM design patterns, performance evaluation and supporting technologies and techniques (i.e. vector stores, model fine-tuning, …)\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Min. 5 year of tech leadership role </span>(Head of Tech, VP Engineering, CTO) <span>in high growth startup</span> plus experience in hiring A-players\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Startup mindset</span> - speed, high agency, resourceful, low ego (company first mindset), and obsessed with creating value\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <span>Our tech stack:</span> We use Postgres, AWS, GCloud, Django, SpringBoot, Flutter, Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD, automatic Tests in Selenium and Pytest, Git, Java, Dart, Python, Terraform. From our Data &amp; AI side Neo4j, Langchain and RAG are relevant technologies.\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <h4><span><span>📍</span> Location &amp; Logistics</span></h4>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>3 days in Office (Berlin or Mannheim, Germany)</div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>Expect regular customer visits</div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Start: </span>As soon as possible\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <span>Compensation: Top of market (incl. equity) </span>(<span>We're constrained by bandwidth, not demand - great time to negotiate</span>)\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div></div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <h4><span>🌍</span> Note from Helena Most, CEO of Resourcly</h4>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>What drives me personally is the deep belief that Germany and Europe’s long-term prosperity and sovereignty depend on a strong, independent economic engine. To secure that future, we need more AI product-first European champions on the global stage - building not just great software, but foundational systems that change how industries operate toda.</div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>My mission is to build one of the world’s biggest automation companies for manufacturing - from Europe. While our headquarters will remain European, our ambition is global. From day one, we benchmark ourselves against the very best in the world and design our product for international scale.</div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>But there’s something deeper that fuels this: the transition to a circular economy. I’ve seen firsthand how complexity in supply chains leads to waste, and how intransparency drives inefficiency - and, inevitably, more waste. In a world of shrinking resources and rising expectations, this is not just an environmental problem - it's a business and economic imperative.</div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>At Resourcly, we’re building the infrastructure to turn unused resources into opportunities, to match supply and demand across silos, and to help manufacturers become more resilient, efficient, and circular - without needing to overhaul their entire systems.</div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>If you share this drive - to make global impact through technology, and to build a more circular, sovereign industrial base for Europe - I’d love to hear from you.</div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div>\n        <div>\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <span>Contact</span>: Helena Most [helena@resourcly.earth;<a tabindex="0" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/helena-most/"><span> LinkedIn</span></a>]\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <span></span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n</main>		https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/resourcly/jobs/53092312-founding-engineer-lead-engineer-m-f-d#content	https://cdn.getro.com/companies/40af9bdb-fa18-5652-90dc-b7c0f8014cb9-1755014750	Resourcly	https://quaint-lathe-5a0.notion.site/Founding-Engineer-Lead-Engineer-20b5b1ab8f0d80e4876cd0be6b54e129?pvs=74&utm_source=Techstars+job+board&utm_medium=getro.com&gh_src=Techstars+job+board	Founding Engineer / Lead Engineer (m/f/d)	1750712400	{"1 - 10 employees","Pre Seed",Senior}	{}
