jects simultaneously</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in creating detailed standard operating procedures</li>\n </ul>\n <p><strong>Preferred Skills:</strong></p>\n <ul>\n  <li>Experience with drones (especially fixed wing), robotics, aerospace, or automotive systems</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of vibration damping and thermal management techniques</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with CFD or FEA tools</li>\n  <li>Familiarity in 3D rendering software such as Keyshot or Solidworks Visualize</li>\n  <li>Experience with iterative design and fast prototyping cycles</li>\n  <li>Comfort using tools such as mills, lathes, and hand tools for prototyping</li>\n  <li>Understanding of various different manufacturing technologies, additive, subtractive, vacuum forming, injection molding, etc.</li>\n </ul>\n <p><strong>What We Offer You:</strong></p>\n <ul>\n  <li>Learning opportunities in a high-demand, cutting-edge field (UAVs / drones)</li>\n  <li>The opportunity to help redefine aviation and contribute to record-breaking flight technologies</li>\n  <li>A meritocratic, collaborative work environment where your contributions are valued</li>\n  <li>Competitive compensation with equity</li>\n </ul>\n</div>		https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/skyfront/jobs/51775828-senior-mechanical-engineer#content	https://cdn.getro.com/companies/83e313a4-c899-59b9-8258-35795a949461-1747359131	Skyfront	https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/senior-mechanical-engineer-at-skyfront-4237007056?utm_source=Techstars+job+board&utm_medium=getro.com&gh_src=Techstars+job+board	Senior Mechanical Engineer	1748552400	{"Aviation & Aerospace",Space,"11 - 50 employees",Senior}	{}
