nimal family members.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>The rich Company holiday schedule includes the week between Christmas and New Year off!</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>We provide a prepaid HRA card for out-of-pocket medical, dental, and vision expenses.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n </ul>\n <p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>All offers of employment at Fideo are contingent upon clear results of a thorough background check. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Fideo is an Equal Opportunity Employer. Fideo does not discriminate on the basis of race, religion, color, sex, gender identity, sexual orientation, age, non-disqualifying physical or mental disability, national origin, veteran status, or any other basis covered by appropriate law.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n <p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>By clicking on the “submit application” button and applying for a job at Fideo, you are agreeing to submit your data to Fideo for the purposes of determining qualification for the role. In addition, Fideo will keep the personal data you submit for future recruiting and hiring processes.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</div>	Software Engineering	https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/fideo-intelligence-2-90ca02c6-83b9-4e7d-94d3-db327e19b097/jobs/51362582-senior-platform-engineer#content	https://cdn.getro.com/companies/36959ca2-2711-5def-849e-04b8bad17492-1755014677	Fideo Intelligence	https://fideointelligence.applytojob.com/apply/fx3XVa8i5N/Senior-Platform-Engineer?utm_source=Techstars+job+board&utm_medium=getro.com&gh_src=Techstars+job+board	Senior Platform Engineer	1747861200	{Security,"1 - 10 employees",Senior}	{Remote}
