ation" dir="ltr"><span>You will be responsible for identifying spacecraft harness requirements for reliable operations with respect to wire, cable and connector types determined currents, voltages, EMI/EMC considerations etc</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>You will be responsible for troubleshooting any issues that arise during the satellite AIT.</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>You will be responsible for documenting the progress in satellite AIT process and the observations during the inspection and validation of the procedures, post implementation, in an enterprise software or via manual record entry.</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>You will be responsible for collaborating with design, systems, and mechanical teams to ensure compliance with technical requirements.</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul> \n    <p dir="ltr"><span>Desirable Skills &amp; Certifications:</span></p> \n    <ul>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>Impeccable communication skills, in English (bonus - Hindi and Kannada), in order to interface between the production team and technicians on a daily basis. </span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>Experience in reading and understanding datasheets, technical reports, wiring diagrams, schematics and test plans is a must.</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>Good Experience in resource and production planning enterprise tools, like SAP, ERP etc. </span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>Highly proficient in documentation and planning tools like Google office (Docs, Sheets), MS projects, Jira, etc. </span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>Understanding of concepts involved in electrical integration and processes, with strong command over all required tools of the trade. </span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>Strong experience and proficiency in understanding and maintaining test equipment, including but not limited to, power supplies, oscilloscopes, current monitors, loads, multimeters, etc </span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>Strong understanding of test campaigns and ability to quickly and accurately document test reports and results. Good understanding of satellite environmental testing is required. </span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>Knowledge of ESD phenomena,cleanroom procedures, standards and best practices to prevent ESD, surface cleaning and preparation processes would be a bonus.</span><span> </span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">\n      <p role="presentation" dir="ltr"><span>Certification from organizations like ISRO any topics related to Electrical and Electronics domain of spacecrafts and satellites</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul> \n    <p dir="ltr"><span>Candidate Acumen: </span></p> \n    <p dir="ltr"><span>A strong desire to work in an unstructured, high-growth, fast-paced start-up environment. Ability to deal with challenges and work out innovative solutions to tackle them. Building a team and guiding them towards success.</span><span>\n      <br>\n     </span><span>\n      <br>\n     </span><span>Benefits:</span><span>\n      <br>\n     </span><span>Health insurance coverage</span><span>\n      <br>\n     </span><span>Unlimited leaves &amp; flexible working hours</span><span>\n      <br>\n     </span><span>Role-based remote work and work-from-home benefi